From 1791e3ade84a462667dbc52186f268f424d8580f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 1 May 2026 06:55:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix TypeScript strict-mode errors; add release Makefile

- Add 'override' modifiers to TreeItem subclass parameter properties
  in playbookProvider.ts (required by noImplicitOverride)
- Add non-null assertions on array accesses already guarded by length
  checks above (required by noUncheckedIndexedAccess) in
  inventoryDetector.ts, playbookDetector.ts, playbookProvider.ts,
  runner.ts
- Add Makefile to .vscodeignore so it isn't bundled into the .vsix
- Add release Makefile with 'gh'-CLI-based release flow:
  make release-current / release-patch / release-minor / release-major
---
